state_and_hooks.content:
useState huki holatni boshqaradi. Hisoblagich misoli:
jsx
import React, { useState } from "react";
function Counter() {
  const [count, setCount] = useState(0);
  return (
    <div>
      <p>Hisoblagich: {count}</p>
      <button onClick={() => setCount(count + 1)}>Oshirish</button>
    </div>
  );
}

events_and_handlers.content:
React-da hodisa ishlovchilari onClick kabi atributlar orqali ishlatiladi. Misol:
jsx
function Button() {
  const handleClick = () => alert("Tugma bosildi!");
  return <button onClick={handleClick}>Meni bos</button>;
}
